{"tid":2463006,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王家衛: 香港電影已死係廢話","createTime":"2021-03-26T11:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T11:15:44.000Z","uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b592513bb51679219bd422934271f912b16c6bef","tid":2463006,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"白粉報唔貼link<br />\n<br />\n曾拍攝《春光乍洩》、《重慶森林》、《花樣年華》等經典電影嘅王家衛，佢早前接受外國傳媒訪問時，被問到點睇「香港電影已死」呢個話題，王導即時發火話︰「我對香港電影已死這廢話感到厭倦，大家都喜歡看電影，講完！（I&rsquo;m tired of all this &lsquo;cinema is dead&rsquo; shit. People enjoy watching movies, period.）」<br />\n<br />\n佢又隨即提出建議，並話︰「現在使大家猶豫不決的是在疫情下看電影的風險和費用，對於真正關心電影業未來的大家，我建議在戲院重開時買一張票，以支持當地的電影院，因為好多戲院都是勉強經營，我們至少要保持這種積極態度。」"},{"pid":"3ae4d7c390e38d2a968f2a439ce7675b0915f92b","tid":2463006,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"又係唔會提政治片<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1dcece798773161c286ad327d38987190fed47","tid":2463006,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9381c343a038d3c583f72743284616f85a1f76f","tid":2463006,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b15ae5972b9205dd783105303f4875648798dc8","tid":2463006,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:13:34.000Z","msg":"條友藍㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6096b23de9fe72f754f62a6f3065c75327a9c6b","tid":2463006,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ae4d7c390e38d2a968f2a439ce7675b0915f92b","tid":2463006,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"又係唔會提政治片<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"